{"word":"G2292 - θαῤῥέω - tharrhéō - thar-hreh'-o - Be bold","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θαῤῥέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>tharrhéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>thar-hreh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be bold"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விசுவாசியாயிரு, தைரியமாயிரு, கண்டிப்பாயிரு, நம்பிக்கை உண்டாக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be of good courage, to be hopeful, confident"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Another form for <a href=\"#/G2293 - θαρσέω - tharséō - thar-seh'-o/2293\">G2293</a>; to <i>exercise courage</i>: - be bold, X boldly, have confidence, be confident. Compare <a href=\"#/G5111 - τολμάω - tolmáō - tol-mah'-o/5111\">G5111</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2292 - θαῤῥέω - tharrhéō - thar-hreh'-o/2292\">G2292</a>, <a href=\"#/G2293 - θαρσέω - tharséō - thar-seh'-o/2293\">G2293</a>"}]}